From ggorj@@@34155694 m@iii@g oii biogii@es@com  Tue Dec  5 11:36:43 2006
From: ggorj@@@34155694 m@iii@g oii biogii@es@com (ggorj@@@34155694 m@iii@g oii biogii@es@com)
Date: 5 Dec 2006 10:36:43 -0000
Subject: [R-sig-DB] binding variable in sqlQuery
Message-ID: <1165315003.2628635600.404.sendItem@bloglines.com>


Try paste() i.e.

my_value = 10
library(RODBC)
inchannel <- odbcConnect("my_server",
uid="samay")
query <- paste("select item1, item2 from _my_table
       
    where item3 >= 10
            and dbid = ", my_value)

sqlQuery(inchannel,
query)



